Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,For俺一人でもステージの上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,巻く上がりは You Know The Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,It's Showtime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出来ないって逸らすその目は
